---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroBanner from "../images/hero3.jpg";
---

<section class="hero" id="hero">
	<div class="hero-content">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h1>De l'incertitude à l'action</h1>
			<p class="quote">
				"Il ne dépend que de vous de suivre la route qui monte et d'éviter celle qui
				descend." – Platon
			</p>
			<p class="section-subtitle">
				Transformez votre vie dès aujourd'hui. Êtes-vous prêt à vous libérer de ce
				qui vous retient, à vous dépasser et à vivre en harmonie avec vos
				aspirations les plus profondes ?
			</p>
		</div>
		<p class="hero-description">
			Il arrive un moment où l'on ne peut plus ignorer les doutes et les schémas
			qui freinent votre épanouissement. Grâce au coaching PNL, je vous accompagne
			pour reprendre le contrôle, transcender vos limites et bâtir la vie que vous
			méritez.
		</p>
		<a href="#contact" class="cta-btn">Le changement commence ici</a>
	</div>
	<Image src={heroBanner} alt="Illustration Hero" class="hero-img" />
</section>

<style lang="scss">
	.hero {
		position: relative;
		height: 90vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		overflow: hidden;

		.hero-content {
			position: relative;
			z-index: 2;
			width: 100%;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: 40px;
			text-align: center;
			text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
			animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;

			&::before {
				content: "";
				position: absolute;
				top: 50%;
				left: 50%;
				width: 130%;
				height: 150%;
				transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
				background: radial-gradient(
					circle,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0%,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 70%
				);
				z-index: -1;
			}
		}

		.section-header {
			margin-bottom: 30px;

			h1 {
				color: $text-white;
				font-size: 4em;
				margin-bottom: 25px;
				font-weight: 800;
				line-height: 1.1;
				position: relative;
				display: inline-block;
				text-shadow:
					2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
					0 0 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
				animation: slideDown 0.8s ease-out;

				&:after {
					content: "";
					position: absolute;
					bottom: -12px;
					left: 50%;
					transform: translateX(-50%);
					width: 120px;
					height: 4px;
					background: linear-gradient(
						90deg,
						rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) 0%,
						rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 50%,
						rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) 100%
					);
					border-radius: 2px;
					animation: expandWidth 1s ease-out;
				}
			}

			.section-subtitle {
				font-size: 1.5em;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 35px auto;
				color: $text-white;
				text-align: justify;
				line-height: 1.6;
				text-shadow:
					1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
					0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
				font-weight: 500;
				animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.3s both;
			}
		}

		.quote {
			font-style: italic;
			font-size: 1.4em;
			color: darken($text-white, 5%);
			margin: 25px 0;
			font-weight: 500;
			opacity: 0.95;
			text-shadow:
				1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
				0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
			animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.6s both;
		}

		.hero-description {
			font-size: 1.3em;
			line-height: 1.7;
			margin: 0 auto 45px;
			color: $text-white;
			text-align: center;
			max-width: 900px;
			font-weight: 500;
			text-shadow:
				1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
				0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
			animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.9s both;
		}

		.cta-btn {
			display: inline-block;
			background: linear-gradient(
				45deg,
				$secondary-color 0%,
				adjust-hue($secondary-color, 15deg) 100%
			);
			color: $text-white;
			padding: 20px 48px;
			text-decoration: none;
			border-radius: 50px;
			font-weight: bold;
			font-size: 1.3em;
			transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
			box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
			letter-spacing: 0.5px;
			animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 1.2s both;
			border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);

			&:hover {
				transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
				box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
				border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
			}

			&:active {
				transform: translateY(-1px);
			}
		}

		.hero-img {
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 100%;
			height: 100%;
			object-fit: cover;
			z-index: 1;
			opacity: 0.7;
			animation: zoomIn 20s ease-out infinite alternate;
		}

		&::before {
			content: "";
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 100%;
			height: 100%;
			background: linear-gradient(
				180deg,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) 0%,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 25%,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 75%,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) 100%
			);
			z-index: 1;
		}

		// Add a top gradient for better text contrast at the top
		&::after {
			content: "";
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 100%;
			height: 30vh;
			background: linear-gradient(
				to bottom,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6) 0%,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 100%
			);
			z-index: 1;
		}
	}

	@keyframes fadeIn {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(20px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}

	@keyframes slideDown {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(-30px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}

	@keyframes expandWidth {
		from {
			width: 0;
		}
		to {
			width: 120px;
		}
	}

	@keyframes zoomIn {
		from {
			transform: scale(1);
		}
		to {
			transform: scale(1.1);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: $mobile) {
		.hero {
			height: 100vh;
			min-height: 100vh;

			.hero-content {
				padding: 25px;
				margin: 0 15px;
			}

			.section-header {
				h1 {
					font-size: 2.8em;
				}

				.section-subtitle {
					font-size: 1.2em;
					padding: 0 20px;
				}
			}

			.cta-btn {
				padding: 16px 32px;
				font-size: 1.1em;
				width: auto;
				min-width: 250px;
			}
		}
	}
</style>
